snippet.title: PixelJunk Presents "Eden Obscura" (Teaser)
snippet.description:
Q-Games is pleased to announce our brand new project Eden Obscura for iOS and Android! The critically acclaimed and award-winning Playstation 3 classic PixelJunk™ Eden is back! 

Once again, Japanese multimedia auteur Baiyon has taken the reins to create an all new audiovisual treasure.



For more, follow us:

http://www.q-games.com/
https://twitter.com/pixeljunknews
